Simple command line interface for the Funcube Dongle Pro and Pro+.

To build for Funcube Dongle Pro type "make" (without the quotes).
To build for Funcube Dongle Pro+ type "make fcdpp".

Requires libusb-1.0-dev.


This is a simple commandf line utility to set the frequency and gain of
Funcube Dongloe Pro and Pro+ devices.

Written by David Pello EA1IDZ and Alexandru Csete OZ9AEC with
contributions by Pieter-Tjerk, PA3FWM.

Uses FCD HID code from QTHID written by:
Howard Long G6LVB,
Alexandru Csete OZ9AEC, 
Mario Lorenz DL5MLO

